title: Skyrim MegaMods v1-8.rar
description:
SKYRIM MEGAMODS v1 through v8

I did not create any of these mods, I am simply a fan and avid user. After beating Skyrim, I used many of these files to create an entirely new experience in the game to make it different. These mods are great and work fantastic for me, I think other people will enjoy them as well. However, I was so tired of trying to download these files. Some of them took forever to get, since they are only being shared by a few people. So here is what has been created in the MegaMods version thus far, 1-8 packed in a RAR file. Please continue to share this file after you download, for all the other people that want these mods for Skyrim. Thanks - Daddyo
